{"tid":1235152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[DEADLINE公投] 今　日　打　禮　賓　—　正評／唔　升　—　負評","createTime":"2019-06-17T05:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T06:14:32.000Z","uid":154486,"like":99,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac589086a8be35c00a664f9bb39e4518b41d3f48","tid":1235152,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"既然大家都覺得開始膠著<br />\n係時候再黎多次連登公投<br />\n如果有大比數過左，我地正式出通牒文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為左二百萬人<br />\n為左梁烈士<br />\n要求林鄭當面對質，否則攻入禮賓府</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>投左要打既人請注意，我地今次要多Ｄ時間先準備到<br />\n所以起碼四點打後齊物資先可以開波<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日打禮賓 - 正評</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好打住 - 負評</span>"},{"pid":"f1d9cb6732a1bae9674ded637266f3561fb3501a","tid":1235152,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c334ba50663666b9b2cfe204bcf0938e670b255f","tid":1235152,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f62865e8f2d389ac6f5887f5f9d6de32a8810d3","tid":1235152,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:24:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"715be2a2199a8dc1937ef3d3a30d75a15bad843f","tid":1235152,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07a205e599cf892d8c73923c9f59b1972dfb65ee","tid":1235152,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bf92e310b67369cdf8d27934e998d6afddb9fe5","tid":1235152,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:26:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78d145cac4d5624018c8911893caba93a08fbe96","tid":1235152,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:27:02.000Z